{"submission_id":"sub_57f6af0a358659b7","run_id":"2026-06-23T16-01-43-649Z_1373642-256d6b3e_ingest_meeting-doc-163061","submitted_at":"2026-06-23T16:07:58.889Z","tool_args_sha256":"sha256:57f6af0a358659b7e17aab5159d4282a2581c374d12211b0c63bd5f1c9ff51d7","schema_version":2,"tool_args":{"source_id":"meeting_doc_163061","observation_kind":"claim","local_observation_id":"claim_meeting_doc_163061_program_desc","label":"Fuel Hedging Program Description","raw_text":"MTA's fuel hedging program mitigates budget risk by dollar cost averaging approximately 50% of projected fuel expenses. The goal of the program is to be 50% hedged for the next 12 months. Monthly hedges are equal to approximately 4% of the projected fuel purchases expected to occur 13-24 months from each hedge execution date. The actual percentage hedged could be higher or lower than the 50% target depending on the actual levels of fuel consumption. While the fuel hedging program includes compressed natural gas, there are currently no active hedges.","payload":{"claim_text":"MTA's fuel hedging program mitigates budget risk by dollar cost averaging approximately 50% of projected fuel expenses. The goal of the program is to be 50% hedged for the next 12 months. Monthly hedges are equal to approximately 4% of the projected fuel purchases expected to occur 13-24 months from each hedge execution date. The actual percentage hedged could be higher or lower than the 50% target depending on the actual levels of fuel consumption. While the fuel hedging program includes compressed natural gas, there are currently no active hedges.","subject":"MTA Fuel Hedging Program","data_type":"program description","data_type_normalized":{"raw_text":"program description","normalized_value":"program_description"}},"evidence_refs":[{"source_id":"meeting_doc_163061","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_163061#p001_b0033","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_163061/blocks.jsonl","page_number":1,"block_id":"p001_b0033","text_sha256":"sha256:f9f8a173491325bc61eed9bcff5d0fe8101aeed749a041302f323222ab2db6e4","text_source":"raw_text"}]},"validation":{"state":"accepted","issues":[]}}
